{"tid":597864,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"散熱膏討論","createTime":"2018-03-19T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T12:17:31.000Z","uid":131980,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c27be08304937ec394045dbbb34cbb0ef29b6e","tid":597864,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"可能好多人會即刻入來講，仲用咩散熱膏，液態鎵is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，散熱效能一定比散熱膏好。<br />\n<br />\n我無錢買，唯有玩住散熱膏先，今日想討論下有關散熱膏幾個問題，歡迎發表偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1:貴嘅散熱膏vs平嘅液態金屬<br />\n2:散熱膏散熱效果我考慮左油性，水性，金屬含量，粒子密度。邊樣最影響導熱性能?<br />\n3:劣質散熱膏可以點劣法<br />\n<br />\n我用過劣質款，價錢係平但導熱性真係差撚到仆街，拆開睇啲空隙大個個地下，應該係話根本唔係空隙，係一個個印，只有少量散熱膏相互接觸。"},{"pid":"6b647c0fd76092fffc5fc6afed934b75ccb34f6d","tid":597864,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"睇唔明，加左都有罅？"},{"pid":"67e351c8241a52c325be32b7b824008d5f11e332","tid":597864,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b647c0fd76092fffc5fc6afed934b75ccb34f6d","tid":597864,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"睇唔明，加左都有罅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"陣間影比你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6711424700726dfdfbe7ffbcde2b6a6b318ef20f","tid":597864,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"Intel既話用咩散熱膏都冇用<br />\n換走啲牙膏先有討論空間"},{"pid":"da4275759810f453d570809760f0df1d1ec39510","tid":597864,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6711424700726dfdfbe7ffbcde2b6a6b318ef20f","tid":597864,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"Intel既話用咩散熱膏都冇用<br />\n換走啲牙膏先有討論空間"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:40:03.000Z","msg":"gpu呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}